[ event handler ]
- event handler using https://blog.keha.dev/posts/cpp20-class-as-non-type-template-param/
	event_handler<{ "resize", void(u32, u32) }, { "created", void() }>
	on("resize" | "created", []((u32, u32 | /* empty */){ /* event cb */ })
